data.description:
Discover the epitome of comfortable living in the heart of Suntree with this recently updated 3-bedroom, 2-bath lakefront pool home. The kitchen boasts elegant granite countertops and sleek black appliances. Unwind in the primary bathroom, complete with a walk-in closet, double sinks, a shower, and a luxurious jacuzzi tub.
Beyond the formal living and dining areas, this residence offers a spacious family room where you can relax and enjoy the ambiance of a modern color-changing fireplace. The beautifully landscaped yard features a paver driveway and a variety of fruit trees, including a sizable mango, lemon, and banana.
Step into the screened-in pool area with a trussed patio, pavers, and a soothing waterfall feature. Security is prioritized with a comprehensive security system included. Conveniently located near Viera shopping and restaurants, this home combines modern comfort with a touch of paradise. Don't miss the chance to call this your home!
